O_INPUTL - Read string from terminal (variable buffer length)

Function: 0357h

Args:
  RF - Pointer to input buffer
  RC - Maximum allowed input characters
  RE.1 - Baud constant

Returns:
  DF=0 - Input finished with <ENTER>
  DF=1 - Input finished with <CTRL><C>

Note: Vector to read string via f_inputl bios function.
